insert into BOOK values (988, "Lift The Flaps: Human Body (Discovery Lift The Flaps)", 118000.0, 88500.0, false, false, false, false, true, current_timestamp(), 88, "Lift The Flaps: Human Body (Discovery Lift The Flaps);Lift the flaps to discover the hidden world inside your body, from your hair to your toenails. Find out what really goes on underneath your skin, with unbelievable facts and amazing drawings that show you how your body works.;", "Lift The Flaps: Human Body (Discovery Lift The Flaps);Lift the flaps to discover the hidden world inside your body, from your hair to your toenails. Find out what really goes on underneath your skin, with unbelievable facts and amazing drawings that show you how your body works.;", 34, 38);
insert into BOOK values (989, "Our Discovery Island American Wb5 W/Cd", 115000.0, 109250.0, false, false, false, false, true, current_timestamp(), 88, "Welcome to Our Discovery Island, a six-level primary series that engages children in 21st century learning. Children uncover clues and solve mysteries as they learn English. Our Discovery Island is a groundbreaking new course that makes learning English an exciting and engaging experience.;;", "Welcome to Our Discovery Island, a six-level primary series that engages children in 21st century learning. Children uncover clues and solve mysteries as they learn English. Our Discovery Island is a groundbreaking new course that makes learning English an exciting and engaging experience.;;", 144, 38);
